thread.title: Resources sector: bouncing along the bottom
thread.title_full: Resources sector: bouncing along the bottom | Business Spectator

author: Barry Fitgerald & Matt Chambers & Eric George
title: Resources sector: bouncing along the bottom
text:
A strange sense of calm has come over Australia's resources sector after a punishing year, rallying most major stocks well above their 12-month lows. But investors have been stung before by the promise of relief. Have commodities finally found their floor?
In this debut episode of Themes and Trends, Barry Fitzgerald, Matt Chambers and Eric George discuss the state of play in Australia's resources sector.
